FBIS4-15299 "drsov068__a94023" FBIS-SOV-94-068-A Daily Report 8 April 1994 ANNEX Armenia Number of Emigrants Reaches 300,000 Number of Emigrants Reaches 300,000 NC3103162294 Yerevan ARAGIL ELECTRONIC NEWS BULLETIN in English 0702 GMT 31 March 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY NC3103162294 Yerevan ARAGIL ELECTRONIC NEWS BULLETIN English BFN [Text] Yerevan ("Azg" daily -- Noyan Tapan), 03/31/94 -- "Many people emigrate from Armenia non-legally, making their registration extremely difficult", the RA [Republic of Armenia] State Minister Rafael Bagoyan declared during a parliament session on March 29. According to the Minister, some 300,000 people emigrated from Armenia in 1991-93. Mr. Bagoyan reported, a migration service was created at the Ministry of Social Security, a similar structure is planned to be created at the refugees department.
